          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24339517/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24339517/" class="">第8页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49602500/" class=" " title="小白想去散步">小白想去散步</a>
                (想我我会打喷嚏)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24339517">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人们的懒惰甚于怯懦，他们恰恰最惧怕绝对的真诚和坦白可能加于他们的负担。

谁能叫醒一个装睡的人。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-02 00:47</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>人们的懒惰甚于怯懦，他们恰恰最惧怕绝对的真诚和坦白可能加于他们的负担。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>谁能叫醒一个装睡的人。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24339517/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
